    <div class="fl-wrap">
      <!-- Header tipo página de canal -->
      <div class="fl-channel-head">
        <span class="fl-channel-avatar">
          <img src="/favicon.png" alt="" width="512" height="512" />
        </span>
        <div class="fl-channel-id">
          <span class="fl-channel-kicker">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M23.5 6.2a3 3 0 0 0-2.1-2.1C19.5 3.5 12 3.5 12 3.5s-7.5 0-9.4.5A3 3 0 0 0 .5 6.2C0 8.1 0 12 0 12s0 3.9.5 5.8a3 3 0 0 0 2.1 2.1c1.9.6 9.4.6 9.4.6s7.5 0 9.4-.5a3 3 0 0 0 2.1-2.1C24 15.9 24 12 24 12s0-3.9-.5-5.8zM9.5 15.6V8.4l6.3 3.6-6.3 3.6z"/></svg>
            Podcast en YouTube
          </span>
          <h2 class="fl-channel-name">Espacio libre <em>de prejuicios.</em></h2>
          <span class="fl-channel-handle">@FloraCultivamosConciencia · {episodes.length} episodios</span>
        </div>
        <a class="fl-channel-sub" href={`${ytChannel}?sub_confirmation=1`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          Suscribirte
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="fl-channel-lead">
        Entrevistas entre Guillermo Sandoval —presidente de Flora ONG— y nuestro director médico, el Dr. Ezequiel Kalb, para hablar sin vueltas de cannabis medicinal. Dale play acá o entrá al canal.
      </p>

      <!-- Episodios estilo YouTube -->
      <ul class="fl-channel-eps" role="list">
        {episodes.map((ep, i) => (
          <li class="fl-ep">
            <button
              class="yt-facade fl-ep-thumb"
              data-id={ep.id}
              data-title={ep.title}
              aria-label={`Reproducir: ${ep.title}`}
            >
              <img
                class="yt-thumb"
                src={`https://i.ytimg.com/vi/${ep.id}/hqdefault.jpg`}
                alt={`Miniatura del episodio ${ep.title}`}
                loading="lazy"
                width="480"
                height="360"
              />
              <span class="fl-ep-play" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M8 5v14l11-7z"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="yt-dur" aria-hidden="true">{ep.dur}</span>
            </button>
            <div class="fl-ep-meta">
              <h3 class="fl-ep-title">{ep.title}</h3>
              <span class="fl-ep-sub">Episodio {String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')} · {ep.dur}</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

